## рџ”Ґ `this` Binding Priority Order (Must Memorize)

1пёЏвѓЈ `new` binding  
2пёЏвѓЈ Explicit binding (`call`, `apply`, `bind`)  
3пёЏвѓЈ Implicit binding (object method)  
4пёЏвѓЈ Default binding (global / undefined)

***

## вњ… Summary Table (Interview Gold)

